\int_{-x}^1 1 d y,-1<x \leq 0, \\
\int_x^1 1 d y, 0<x<1, \\
0, \text { 其它, }
\end{array}=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
1+x,-1<x \leq 0, \\
1-x, 0<x<1, \\
0, \text { 其它, }
